		W-MAIL Local Mail Agent (MINIX)

		     MicroWalt W-MAIL V2.5
		     =====================

This archive contains the sources of the W-MAIL program;
which is a MINIX version of the MAILX program available
on most UNIXes.

It does not need the presence of UUCP in order to run.
However, for non-local mail delivery a remote mailer
(like MicroWalt UMAIL) is required to be present.

Enjoy!
